ty.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ysmiles would like to thank the love, trust and companionship of many guests who have been using the service at Ysmiles. Hopefully, along with its development, Ysmiles Dental Clinic will always receive the trust and support of customers in the near future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>--&gt; Once again Ysmiles would like to thank and invite customers to celebrate the grand opening and receive attractive offers from our new branch 3- Masteri An Phu, District 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Best regards.</p>\r\n', '', 'mung-ngay-khai-truong-chop-ngay-uu-dai-lon', '/backend/web/uploads/images/318498085_537005331776825_4293275567316186250_n.jpg', NULL, 1, 0, 55, 0, '', NULL, 'MỪNG NGÀY KHAI TRƯƠNG- CHỚP NGAY ƯU ĐÃI LỚN ️', 'Tưng bừng KHAI TRƯƠNG CHI NHÁNH 3 tại Masteri An Phú-Quận 2, NHA KHOA THẨM MỸ YSMILES gửi tặng đến quý khách hàng chương trình ngày khuyến mãi vô cùng đặc biệt.', 'ysmiles, nhakhoathammy , nha khoa , nha khoa thẩm mỹ', '2022-12-22 22:46:09');
