mes New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">C&aacute;c loại răng sứ hiện nay </span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">1.&nbsp; Răng to&agrave;n sứ</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">+ Tự nhi&ecirc;n, trắng đẹp, kh&ocirc;ng đổi m&agrave;u, kh&ocirc;ng g&acirc;y dị ứng.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">+ Chất liệu tạo sứ được l&agrave;m bằng vật liệu c&ocirc;ng nghệ cao, khả năng chịu lực tốt v&agrave; độ bền l&acirc;u d&agrave;i.</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"line-height